$ON_ZTRANTYPE
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZTRANTYPE From W1NCSA
Return

$AV_ZTRANTYPE
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"ATABDIV","LNGDES","807",num$([M]TRANTYPE(indice))) From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
Return

$CHG_STY
Return


